---
---
<section id="intro" class="h-screen w-full snap-start flex items-center justify-center bg-dark-bg relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative background glow -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-600/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-indigo-600/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="text-center z-10 px-6">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold mb-6 tracking-tight drop-shadow-lg">
      Hello, I'm <span class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-400 to-indigo-400 text-transparent bg-clip-text">Lee Jinwoo</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-300 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      5년 차 시니어 프론트엔드 개발자. <br class="hidden md:block"/>
      사용자 중심의 경험과 견고한 아키텍처를 지향합니다.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 opacity-80 animate-bounce">
      <a href="#career" aria-label="Scroll to Career" class="inline-flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <span>Scroll Down</span>
        <i class="pi pi-arrow-down text-xl"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
